//   style = {{vnf_vertex_array()}} style used to triangulate heightfield textures.  Default: "min_edge"
//   anchor = Translate so anchor point is at origin (0,0,0).  See [anchor](attachments.scad#subsection-anchor).  Default: `CENTER`
